        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="t3_note" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Key Data Flow:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. SENSE detects David&#39;s state from conversations&lt;br&gt;2. PREDICT mines patterns → briefing&lt;br&gt;3. ACT triggers proactive care (Telegram/chat)&lt;br&gt;4. UNDERSTAND extracts emotions + learnings per conversation pair&lt;br&gt;5. EVALUATE scores quality (3 dims: helpful, relevant, emotional)&lt;br&gt;6. COMPARE generates A/B test + DPO pairs&lt;br&gt;7. LEARN tunes adaptation rules from reward signals&lt;/font&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fillColor=#F9FAFB;strokeColor=#E5E7EB;rounded=1;fontSize=10;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
